      1          /**
      2           * @file
      3           * @brief       Evaluate a post-fix equation defined in a setting file displacement.
      4           *
      5           * @details     This module evaluates a mathematical equation defined in the setting file and
      6           *              returns the result. The result can be used as a TRUE/FALSE condition.
      7           *
      8           *              If any error occurs during the evaluation, the module returns 0 (FALSE) and
      9           *              logs an exception message.
     10           *
     11           * @copyright   Copyright 2020 Whirlpool Corporation.  All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL.
     12           */
